Michael Lucas  (  born Andrei Lvovich Treivas , March 10 , 1972 in Moscow , Russian SFSR  )  is a Russian -- Israeli-American gay pornographic film actor , director , activist , writer and the founder/CEO of Lucas Entertainment , New York City 's largest gay-adult-film company .
